Scheduling and Course Request
**1st Task** -->  Make sure in core you have set up the years and terms for the following year.
Go to Core --> settings --> School Information --> years & Terms 
Term Name: 1st
Description: Semester
Sort Order: 10
Start Date: 06/16/year
End Date: 12/19/year
Days to default beyond end date: 16
Previous Year equivalent to roll over from: 1st Semester year - year (ex. 2025-2026) 
[Repeat for 2nd semester BUT]
Term Name: 2nd
Description: Semester
Sort Order: 20
Start Date: 12/20/year
End Date: 06/15/year
Days to default beyond end date: 30
Previous Year equivalent to roll over from: 2nd Semester year - year (ex. 2025-2026)

**2nd Task** -->  In Lion's Den go to Academics --> scheduling request and schedules --> Course Request Setup 
Fill in this to allow for teachers to submitt course request 
[This can also be done by a data import]
Signup Begin: date & time
Signup End: date & time
Recommend	by Teacher
Approve by Manager 
Min Request: 6
Max Request: 8 
Min Enroll: 7

**3rd Task** --> In the same area select the "Offer Course" tab and select which course will be offered. 
*****COMPLETED*****

